Pocket Bandit
-------------

A comic style slot machine game for the Android platform. The game is
modelled after the classic, three reel, ten stops slot machines, made
popular by Mills Novelty.
Unlike it's mechanical cousins, Pocket Bandit is not entirely luck based, but
also offers elements of skill and strategy game play.

PocketBandit depends on libGDX v0.97 or higher. Get it from
http://libgdx.badlogicgames.com/
